headline: Fidelity's Improved Business Mix Is Reflected In Shares (Rating Downgrade)
summary: Fidelity reshaped its portfolio, selling Worldpay and acquiring GPN's Issuer Solutions to improve business mix and earnings quality. See why FIS stock is a Hold.
